@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "About Us";
}
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    @* <link href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet"> *@
    <title>About Us</title>
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #121212;
            color: #ffffff;
        }

        .about-section {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .about-image {
            width: 100%;
            height: auto;
            filter: brightness(0.8); /* Adjust brightness for dark theme */
        }

        .about-text {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

            .about-text p {
                color: #dcdcdc; /* Light grey text for readability */
            }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <img src="/Images/Artboard 2.png" alt="Artwork 1" class="about-image">
    <div class="container about-section">
        
        <div class="about-text">
            <p>
                James Khumalo, a visionary entrepreneur, set out to establish KhumaloCraft Emporium as a global e-commerce platform to showcase handcrafted products. His dream involves connecting artisans worldwide with a discerning audience.
            </p>
            <p>
                Born and raised in the vibrant city of Johannesburg, James always had a keen eye for art and craftsmanship. He spent his early years traveling across South Africa, immersing himself in the diverse cultures and traditional art forms of various communities. This journey ignited his passion for preserving and promoting artisanal crafts.
            </p>
            <p>
                With a background in business and technology, James combined his skills to create KhumaloCraft Emporium. The platform is designed to offer a seamless shopping experience, bringing unique, high-quality handcrafted products to customers worldwide. Under his leadership, KhumaloCraft Emporium has grown into a thriving community that supports and celebrates artisans from different corners of the globe.
            </p>
            <p>
                James believes in the power of storytelling through art. Every product on KhumaloCraft Emporium comes with a story about its maker, providing a personal touch that connects customers with the artisans. James's vision extends beyond commerce; he aims to create a space where art, culture, and commerce converge to empower artists and enrich customers' lives.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.5.1.slim.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@4.5.2/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
